- I don't really know. And neither do you.

77
00:06:53,903 --> 00:06:56,781
No. There's something. I can feel it.

78
00:06:56,863 --> 00:06:59,900
He's different. He's changed.

79
00:07:00,863 --> 00:07:04,936
