You see that? You see how he reacted
when you mentioned Webs?

102
00:08:28,383 --> 00:08:31,261
Cool as Cool Whip.
What's up with that?

103
00:08:31,343 --> 00:08:36,337
The sun's coming up. I need to go and check
on Dawn. We need to keep an eye on Spike.

104
00:08:36,423 --> 00:08:40,177
Whoa, whoa, whoa. When you say "we"
you mean me. Me's gotta go to work.

105
00:08:40,263 --> 00:08:43,494
- I got a big meeting in a couple of hours.
- This is serious.

106
00:08:43,583 --> 00:08:47,337
We cannot let him leave this house
until we know if he's killing again.

107
00:08:47,423 --> 00:08:49,175
We need someone to watch him.

108
00:08:49,263 --> 00:08:52,812
- Uh-uh. Forget it, Harris.
- You said you'd do it on the phone.

109
00:08:52,903 --> 00:08:58,978
