again. You want to leave me alone with him?!

110
00:08:59,063 --> 00:09:02,817
- Didn't mind being alone with him before.
- What was that?

111
00:09:02,903 --> 00:09:08,899
Nothing. Look, we don't actually know
that he's killed anyone. You know, lately.

112
00:09:08,983 --> 00:09:11,861
- Might all just be a mistake.
- But you don't think so.

113
00:09:11,943 --> 00:09:17,176
