169
00:14:27,223 --> 00:14:33,901
I can't stop thinking about you and us
and our brief but unforgettable time together.

170
00:14:34,943 --> 00:14:37,503
I mean, it's...
Why else would I be here?

171
00:14:37,583 --> 00:14:42,782
