that you're some whacked-out serial killer.

172
00:14:42,863 --> 00:14:45,252
I don't know why I said that.
Forget I said that.

173
00:14:45,343 --> 00:14:49,052
It's craziness talking.
It's just nerves. Nerves.

174
00:14:50,463 --> 00:14:53,057
Nerves and... and horniness.

175
00:14:53,143 --> 00:14:57,341
Oh, just shut up, William, and take me.
Take me now.

176
00:15:09,343 --> 00:15:10,822
- Anya.
- Hm?

177
00:15:10,903 --> 00:15:16,660
It's not that I'm not tempted. Obviously,
if things were different, you're a right catch.

178
00:15:17,223 --> 00:15:20,772
I got it. No problem. I understand.

179
00:15:22,343 --> 00:15:24,015
- You think I'm fat.
- What?

180
00:15:24,103 --> 00:15:27,379
- It's either that or the haircut.
- The do's quite fetching.

181
00:15:27,463 --> 00:15:29,931
- Oh, right. Now you like the haircut.
- Love it.

182
00:15:30,023 --> 00:15:33,299
